query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('action',
'applet',
'curl',
'cygwin',
'html-table',
'http-headers',
'jdbc',
'plugins',
'processing',
'sap',
'shell',
'uicollectionview',
'variadic-templates',
'xhtml');
